ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCCOFTA Rules of Origin Regulations
PrecisCCOFTA RULES OF ORIGIN REGULATIONS implement, in Canada, the rules of origin negotiated by Canada and Colombia that will be used to determine when goods have undergone sufficient production to qualify for preferential tariff treatment.
